class MyPoint implements Hashable {
  num x, y;

  MyPoint(this.x, this.y);

  int hashCode() {
    int result = 17;
    result = 37 * result + x.hashCode();
    result = 37 * result + y.hashCode();
    return result;
  }

  String toString() => 'Point(x=' + x.toString() + ',y=' + y.toString() + ')';
}

void main() {
  MyPoint pointA = new MyPoint(1, 2);
  MyPoint pointB = new MyPoint(3, 4);

  Map<MyPoint, String> map = new Map<MyPoint, String>();
  map[pointA] = "valueA";
  map[pointB] = "valueB";

  map.forEach((k,v) => print('$k : $v'));
}
}}}
